org.jpokemon.pokemon.storage

Class PokemonStorageBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpokemon.pokemon.storage.PokemonStorageBlock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<PokemonStorageUnit>

    public class PokemonStorageBlock
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<PokemonStorageUnit>
    A representation of all the PokemonStorageUnits allocated to a Player.

    PokemonStorageBlock supports 1 unit of unique size, to be used for the party. Other units have common size.
